1
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,200
Surprised?

2
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,400
We meet again.

3
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:00,880
You fat bastard.

4
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,120
So you're not dead.

5
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:06,160
Dead my ass!

6
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,520
You wish!

7
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,720
Why did you kill me?

8
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:26,800
Bro Six said so.

9
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,320
You saw something you shouldn't have.

10
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,040
These past few days, Sister Fei

11
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,720
has been looking for Bro Wu Di too.

12
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,960
She wanted to work with him.

13
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,720
That day, I heard fighting upstairs.

14
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,880
So I rushed up and saved you.

15
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,560
Boss!

16
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,040
They got away.

17
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,600
Confused?

18
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,120
Can't figure it out?

19
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,200
Today,

20
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,760
you have to die.

21
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,720
Dawa.

22
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,280
The real mastermind is still out there.

23
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,760
It's not time to reveal the truth yet.

24
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,960
Sorry you had to go through this.

25
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,480
Six.

26
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,360
I messaged Bro Xingchen a while ago.

27
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,640
Had him make a fake security video.

28
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,120
In the footage,

29
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,320
it shows me killing Dawa in a rage.

30
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,760
That video you saw

31
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,640
was fake.

32
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,800
As for Ali,

33
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,400
that was a setup to fool you too.

34
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,680
You jerk.

35
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,760
That stab hurt like hell.

36
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,440
But I liked it.

37
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,360
Be serious.

38
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,360
We have business to do.

39
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,400
Ma Liu.

40
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:54,840
No.

41
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:56,480
I should call you

42
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,880
Assassin Forty-Seven.

43
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,480
Or should I say Sam?

44
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,480
Three years ago,

45
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,880
Country M bought you off, didn't they?

46
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,560
After you got the mission,

47
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:05,080
you got close to Zhao Wu Di.

48
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,640
And became his friend.

49
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,280
Bro Wu Di.

50
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,040
Between zero one and zero nine,

51
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,560
which number hurts the most?

52
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,680
Which number hurts the most?

53
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,680
Zero five, of course.

54
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,280
What a painful realization.

55
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:25,120
Later, Bro Wu Di took out Bald Eagle.

56
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,400
And Country M listed him as a

57
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:28,000
triple-S-level threat.

58
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,680
From now on,

59
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,160
I'll call you A-Di.

60
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,280
Boss.

61
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,400
It's me.

62
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,200
Yes.

63
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,240
He really does have amnesia.

64
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,200
Don't worry.

65
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,480
I'll keep a close eye on him.

66
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,360
You fat bastard.

67
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,240
Nice acting.

68
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,920
You even fooled me.

69
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,320
Ma Liu.

70
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,200
Your family's assets

71
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,600
are at least ten billion.

72
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,440
Just to take me down,

73
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,920
you worked as a guard for three hard years.

74
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,760
Now I finally get it.

75
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,760
Turns out I'm your true love.

76
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,520
Hey!

77
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,320
Who are you flirting with?

78
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:11,760
Honey.

79
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,000
I'm kidding.

80
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,200
You're the one I care about most.

81
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,200
All right.

82
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:28,240
As expected of Zhao Wu Di.

83
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,640
I hid it so well,

84
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,520
and you still found me out.

85
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,240
Ma Liu.

86
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,240
Even the slyest fox

87
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,680
will eventually show its tail.

88
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,360
I've gotta say,

89
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,440
keeping up this act is exhausting.

90
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,440
I'm done pretending.

91
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,360
I'm laying my cards on the table.

92
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,840
Originally,

93
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,080
we could've been real brothers,

94
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:55,280
minding our own business,

95
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,480
and moving forward together.

96
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,080
What a shame.

97
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,840
Now,

98
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,840
only I alone

99
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,240
get to keep going.

100
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,040
Watch out!

101
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,560
He's playing dirty!

102
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,560
Dawa!

103
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,320
Dawa!

104
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:30,600
Dawa!

105
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,920
General Dawa!

106
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,400
Dead for good, huh?

107
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,520
Sorry about that.

108
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,360
Sorry to startle everyone.

109
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:49,880
As the ruler of Dongba,

110
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:50,920
you don't really think

111
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,960
I came here alone, do you?

112
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,640
To tell you the truth,

113
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,040
I have my men stationed all around here.

114
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,720
Monitoring you 24/7.

115
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,680
Every move you make

116
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,240
is under my control.

117
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:03,280
No way.

118
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,960
I checked the perimeter already.

119
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,240
Where would outsiders come from?

120
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,360
Of course they're our own people.

121
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,440
They're familiar faces, after all.

122
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,720
This company's cleaners,

123
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,880
security, and half the staff

124
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,120
were all placed by me.

125
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,680
Boss Ma,

126
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,880
you spent a fortune.

127
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,680
Couldn't be helped.

128
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,120
You're Zhao Wu Di.

129
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,040
To take Dongba,

130
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,840
I hired them all at a huge price.

131
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,440
You know what I'm capable of.

132
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,600
They're no match for me.

133
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,520
Of course I know what you can do.

134
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,080
But what if they used

135
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,560
the same Wushuang technique as you?

136
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,280
Since when?

137
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:59,280
The moment you fell into Dongba's hands,

138
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,400
I'd already gotten

139
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,400
your DNA.

140
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:03,080
And copied your abilities.

141
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,080
Your amnesia

142
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,120
was caused by this too.

143
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,920
Now every one of them is as strong as you.

144
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,880
Maybe even stronger.

145
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,160
Are you kidding me?

146
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,840
Bro Wu Di is one of a kind.

147
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,560
No one can be better than him.

148
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,360
Don't believe it?

149
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,480
Give it a try.

150
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,160
Fine, I'll try it.

151
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:33,720
Bro!

152
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,480
Bro Xingchen is here!

153
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:39,840
Bro Xingchen!

154
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,080
I forgot to tell you.

155
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:41,920
They're using

156
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,040
the enhanced Wushuang.

157
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,400
You can't beat them!

158
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,800
I haven't even warmed up yet.

159
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,200
Tough talk.

160
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,320
Fine, fine, fine.

161
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,480
Wushuang.

162
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,800
Truly unparalleled in this world.

163
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,160
Looks like

164
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,520
you have no more use to me.

165
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,240
Then I'll

166
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,640
stop wasting time.

167
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,640
Ma Liu.

168
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,040
You went through all this trouble to set up this trap,

169
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,760
what was it all for?

170
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,960
Since you're not getting out alive anyway,

171
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,200
I might as well tell you.

172
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,240
What I want is

173
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:20,040
your Black Bat International's

174
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,760
master key to all personnel archives.

175
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,280
Once I get that key,

176
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,960
and combine it with my wealth,

177
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,960
I'll be the king of the world.

178
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,240
No one will dare defy me.

179
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:30,920
So that's your plan.

180
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,160
Hand it over,

181
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:33,240
and I can make it so you

182
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,240
die a quick death.

183
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,240
Ma Liu.

184
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,440
You're such a smart guy,

185
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,120
and you still haven't noticed

186
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,440
I was stalling for time?

187
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,800
What do you mean?

188
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,200
This is luring the snake out of its hole.

189
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,160
First, lay the bait,

190
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:58,640
then cast the net to catch the big fish.

191
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,720
Captain Cangming,

192
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:00,840
Black Bat Special Field Ops,

193
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,760
reporting for backup.

194
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:02,600
Black Bat Assault Team,

195
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,360
reporting for backup.

196
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:05,560
Black Bat Defense Team,

197
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,560
reporting for backup.

198
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:07,880
Black Bat Demolition Unit,

199
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,880
reporting for backup.
